Citation.sAbstract: The solubility of Avermectin B1a in methanol, ethanol, n-propanol, i-propanol, n-butanol, isopropyl ether, and mixed solvents of methanol + water have been measured over the temperature range of (278.2 to 318.2) K at atmospheric pressure. The experimental solubility data was correlated with the Apelblat equation.
Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Avermectin B1a in Some Pure and Mixed Solvents from (278.2 to 318.2) K
